result.name: The Chop House

reviews.text: Food, environment and service are good here with a fair price. They offered Happy Hour for drinks. The oysters are okay and I felt that cooler the better. The mixed grill meat is nice. The lamp chop is the best in this dish. The MAC n Cheese is excellent! Taste and smell are really well. But sad the dessert I want to order is sold out...

Different menu from inside and outdoor seating!

Outside: all time happy hour ~$50/drink. Recommend belly pork pizza, french fries and chicken wings. awful experience for mussel, please dont try: small in size, no texture and not hot enough for serving. Can also order inside menu as wel. But not aircondition.

Inside : happy hr from 4~8 ~$60+/drink, standard menu.
One star is overrated. Service is sucks. Don't understand instructions to cook a steak. Overpriced for the service and food quality.
My favorite spot at TST... try it then you will know
There is a big outdoor area, but indoor seating is more popular in summer time
